text: Kaltovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kaltovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 714 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Iglino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Kaltovka
